  <h2>What Makes a 3-in-1 Steam Brush Different From a Regular Deshedding Tool?</h2>
  <p>Most deshedding brushes do one thing: drag loose fur to the surface using metal or plastic tines. The 3-in-1 Steam Pet Grooming Brush adds two features that change how the session goes. A built-in steam function warms the coat and loosens the undercoat before the bristles touch it — reducing pulling resistance that makes cats squirm. Soft silicone nubs mimic a massage rather than a rake, which is why these brushes went viral on TikTok: cats that normally flee during grooming lean into them.</p>
